      <title>俄勒冈州和华盛顿州袭击投票箱的凶手被通缉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/ballot-box-arsonist-sought-in-oregon-and-washington-attacks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[警方公布了俄勒冈州和华盛顿州两起投票箱起火事件嫌疑人的描述，目前选举官员正紧急向受影响的选民发送替换选票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/ballot-box-arsonist-sought-in-oregon-and-washington-attacks</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 18:27:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尼日利亚各州拒绝 Tinubu 的税收改革，对税收计划造成打击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/nigerian-state-governors-reject-tinubu-s-tax-reforms-in-blow-to-revenue-drive</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尼日利亚各州长要求撤回修改国家税法的立法，这对总统博拉·蒂努布增加收入以填补不断扩大的支出缺口的努力造成了打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/nigerian-state-governors-reject-tinubu-s-tax-reforms-in-blow-to-revenue-drive</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 18:06:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>奥尔班计划给欧盟领导人带来特朗普惊喜 引发担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/orban-stirs-up-concerns-he-plans-a-trump-surprise-for-eu-leaders</link>
      <description><![CDATA[维克托·奥尔班周四与唐纳德·特朗普进行了电话交谈，这引起一些欧盟官员的担忧，他们担心，如果匈牙利总理赢得下周的美国大选，他可能计划邀请他参加即将召开的欧盟会议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/orban-stirs-up-concerns-he-plans-a-trump-surprise-for-eu-leaders</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 17:46:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加州将测试选民的勇气，寻求发行 200 亿美元债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/squeamish-california-voters-face-most-state-bonds-since-2006</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加州将于下周询问选民是否应该再借 200 亿美元用于学校和气候变化项目，这是近二十年来该州在单次选举中被要求批准的最多数额的州债券。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/squeamish-california-voters-face-most-state-bonds-since-2006</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 15:41:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈里斯抓住特朗普保护女性的誓言，无论她们“喜欢与否”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/harris-hits-trump-vow-to-protect-women-if-they-like-it-or-not</link>
      <description><![CDATA[副总统卡马拉·哈里斯抓住唐纳德·特朗普的言论不放，特朗普称，如果当选，他将“保护”女性，无论她们“喜欢与否”，以此攻击其共和党对手在生殖权利和其他自由方面的立场，以吸引郊区和独立女性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/harris-hits-trump-vow-to-protect-women-if-they-like-it-or-not</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 15:38:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩尔多瓦最高法院批准支持欧盟的公投，对俄罗斯造成打击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/moldova-s-top-court-clears-pro-eu-referendum-in-blow-to-russia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩尔多瓦最高法院批准了最近举行的全民公投的结果，驳回了亲俄反对派关于此次投票存在缺陷的指控，摩尔多瓦加入欧盟的计划将写入该国宪法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/moldova-s-top-court-clears-pro-eu-referendum-in-blow-to-russia</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 15:29:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
