      <title>摇摆州的印度裔美国人成为民主党目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/kamala-harris-campaign-targets-new-indian-american-voters-in-key-swing-states</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一个阳光明媚的星期天下午，两名男子在佐治亚州福赛斯县的一个街区挨家挨户走访，为民主党争取选票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/kamala-harris-campaign-targets-new-indian-american-voters-in-key-swing-states</guid>
